{"tid":598163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁耀忠：譚耀宗言論得人驚","createTime":"2018-03-19T09:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T15:56:52.000Z","uid":72621,"like":3,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8fd889fea735d49c3cbb3b65f207d8db021fa8a4","tid":598163,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:34:28.000Z","msg":"梁耀忠：譚耀宗言論得人驚<br />\n<br />\n支聯會常委梁耀忠形容譚耀宗言論「得人驚」，坦言「不知道需不需要擔心」。他認為有關口號並非今天才出現，而是多年來社會大眾一直都接受，認為若此事屬實，重點並非不是他作為支聯會常委，其議員資格會否被質疑，而是對於社會言論自由的抹殺，「若果是說港獨分裂國家（和《基本法》）有抵觸，都勉強可以講通，但如果要在這個層面說是違反，則是不符合『一國兩制』的原則」。<br />\n<br />\n被問到若譚耀宗所言屬實，會否退出支聯會或者不再說類似言論，梁耀忠就指「未作考慮」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/港聞/169622/譚耀宗指叫-結束一黨專政-或違憲-支聯會-六四集會續呼口號\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2F169622%2F%E8%AD%9A%E8%80%80%E5%AE%97%E6%8C%87%E5%8F%AB-%E7%B5%90%E6%9D%9F%E4%B8%80%E9%BB%A8%E5%B0%88%E6%94%BF-%E6%88%96%E9%81%95%E6%86%B2-%E6%94%AF%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83-%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83%E7%BA%8C%E5%91%BC%E5%8F%A3%E8%99%9F&d=dYNBpw77B42fMm44Tyl9pxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=8b6bb8d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/港聞/169622/譚耀宗指叫-結束一黨專政-或違憲-支聯會-六四集會續呼口號</a><br />\n<br />\n忠路拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4502beb5b43b984f03493fd04724622a2a97a65","tid":598163,"uid":47202,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:36:18.000Z","msg":"dq天琦冇問題, dq我地泛民就得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4fdd358634491131d36062ee9f143a53e2809de","tid":598163,"uid":60545,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b4502beb5b43b984f03493fd04724622a2a97a65","tid":598163,"uid":47202,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:36:18.000Z","msg":"dq天琦冇問題, dq我地泛民就得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:37:39.000Z","msg":"泛民：佢地係鬼！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b38da9633562ac07085ab9dcbf7994d8c75ffa","tid":598163,"uid":47359,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:37:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔夠梁耀忠讓位畀梁君彥咁得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n2016-2017年度立會傑出柒頭: 梁耀忠<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/456906/5?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/456906/5?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},{"pid":"73d9a28f1445dbaf13b340e819cb3c2d64af528a","tid":598163,"uid":72621,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b4fdd358634491131d36062ee9f143a53e2809de","tid":598163,"uid":60545,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b4502beb5b43b984f03493fd04724622a2a97a65","tid":598163,"uid":47202,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:36:18.000Z","msg":"dq天琦冇問題, dq我地泛民就得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:37:39.000Z","msg":"泛民：佢地係鬼！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:38:50.000Z","msg":"唔比講一黨專政咪退出支那會唔講<br />\n議席大過天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"147796827c8301f816f8b2ede0586614b808fbeb","tid":598163,"uid":76488,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:39:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"020475ac7602d75781201de1b960ca21222c10e9","tid":598163,"uid":120821,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:46:57.000Z","msg":"如果唔係呢條on 9手渣煙2同花順都pass個主席位出來，何來d